item.title: ICUAFC 1s conquering London
item.author: Christian Nielsen,Henry Garner,
item.description: On the 27th of October the “ICUAFC elite” (Tofis, 2012) ventured north of the wall to a place so windy that Dorothy and Toto thanked their lucky stars that they live in Kansas: Shenley. The opposition were the old enemy and second best university in London, UCL. A fixture steeped in history, this …
